{
  "stem": "13395.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he stood on that car, and he says, I have-- you are free now.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I beg you, don't tell my soldiers where the camp is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "These are men that were now in the war for so long.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They will rape any woman they see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, but we are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are the victims.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're not Germans.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, I can't guarantee you safety.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we all retreated back in the barracks, closed the doors, moved the bunk beds to the doors and to the windows, and sat there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The same night, somebody tried to get in and kicked in the door, couldn't move it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And 45 women in one room started to scream.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he started to run away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The reason that we screamed, we didn't know if the guy is inside or out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were two, three people in one bed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if she happened to have-- a friend happened to have your hand on you or near you, you didn't know who it was in that moment.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You thought it would be full of Russians in our room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, we screamed so much, that they run away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we came up with an idea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We wrote-- found a piece of paper and some pencils in the SS guards' offices.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we wrote 'Typhoid Fever' and put it on every door.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the next night when they came, they ran away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that saved us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This is why I say women's experiences are different than those of men.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Here were the liberators, when they liberated as a camp Buchenwald and Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The Americans and the British rolled in with the truck with the food and with the medication and with the doctors.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had to hide, afraid to be raped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That was our liberation.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
